{
  "stem": "25114.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Yeah, tents from straw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We gathered straw.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were warm.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We put some straw in the-- in the bottom, we covered with peasant's rags-- and that's how I-- rags-- and that's how I slept, with my husband, and one of those.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was warm.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was still end of-- it was early autumn.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everything was in the fields-- there had lots of honey and lots of-- we had chickens and we had-- they brought some vegetables from the thing, and it was quiet, you know?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Quite a good life for this time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And only thing that I wasn't well, but nothing could be done about it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One day when my husband went on a mission first thing in the morning, at 5 o'clock I woke up the doctor and saying that I can't stand it anymore.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You've got to operate on me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he took off-- everybody was still asleep, apart from the watch.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a fire burning, so he took a bit of a box of a few what he had, scissors and things like that, that are primitive instruments.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He boiled them in the-- in the fire, and he opened up my breast and took out all the-- what was in it, lots of ulcer, sort of pus, and things like this.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, if he only had a few-- at this time it was called-- it wasn't antibiotics, it was something else.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Strepto-something, streptosist or something-- they call it, this little red tablet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I could save your life, and in other case, we'll just have to-- to wait and see.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'll do my best.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
